00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:09,439 --> 00:01:10,319
How long has she been asleep?

2
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:12,519
A whole day now.

3
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,280
We need to speed up the tournament.

4
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,879
Go tell Limpy.

5
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,519
Tell him that during the semifinals,

6
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,599
he must forfeit outright for Frostwind City.

7
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,319
That'll save us a round.

8
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,640
Tongtong

9
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,280
can't hold on much longer.

10
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:31,359
For the next couple of days,

11
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,599
you should rest up too.

12
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,879
That Immortal Artifact

13
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,319
won't be easy to get.

14
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:46,640
Friendship first,

15
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,319
competition second.

16
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,319
Milk tea's on me, everyone.

17
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:54,920
What a coincidence.

18
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,359
I prepared milk tea

19
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,599
for our friends from Qiushui City too.

20
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,719
Don't be shy.

21
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:07,959
Please.

22
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:10,560
Your milk tea

23
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,039
is way too cheap.

24
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,439
My teammates

25
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,639
wouldn't bother with it.

26
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,759
My teammates hate the rich by nature.

27
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,240
They can't stomach expensive stuff.

28
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:23,240
Then do you dare drink mine?

29
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:27,520
Do you dare drink mine?

30
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,439
Let's drink together.

31
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,400
Let's give a warm round of applause

32
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,919
as we welcome Shanhai City,

33
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,319
Qiushui City,

34
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,479
Xingguang City,

35
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,120
and Frostwind City's contestants

36
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,319
to the stage to draw lots.

37
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,680
The semifinal rules are:

38
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:51,439
Number one faces number two,

39
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:53,199
and three faces four.

40
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:56,000
That junk lantern you gave me last time

41
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,560
was complete garbage.

42
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:58,800
You're screwed.

43
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,639
I can't beat you.

44
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,479
But Fatty Geng wants me to fight you.

45
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,479
And I'm afraid of pain.

46
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,400
So...

47
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,960
Surrendering outright is too embarrassing.

48
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,560
How about you lightly hit me a few times,

49
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,159
and then I'll fly off the stage.

50
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,120
The reward?

51
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,240
The reward is,

52
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,840
just the two of us settle it.

53
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,639
No other teammates need to fight.

54
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,439
That way, Shanhai City

55
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,759
goes straight to the finals.

56
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:22,560
Deal.

57
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:25,319
Hey, you two,

58
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,680
I'm still standing here.

59
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,159
Why haven't you left the stage yet?

60
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:30,960
You haven't drawn yet.

61
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,719
How am I supposed to leave?

62
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,319
Just cheat like last time.

63
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:39,319
Well, you've gotta draw one first.

64
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,000
Get back here.

65
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,199
Shanhai City, once again,

66
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:55,319
has drawn the first match slot.

67
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,479
Keeping their record going,

68
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:58,919
I'd like to call them

69
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,319
the King of the First Match.

70
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:12,280
The first match

71
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,919
will be number one Shanhai City

72
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:16,519
versus number two Qiushui City.

73
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,600
Let the match begin.

74
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:26,120
Watch us crush you this time.

75
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,439
As if you could.

76
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,480
Damn fatty.

77
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,319
By the way,

78
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:46,120
how much stuff did you slip into my drink?

79
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,199
Just a tiny bit.

80
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,839
Bullshit.

81
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,399
Even though it's a fake fight,

82
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,319
we still gotta make it look real.

83
00:04:58,399 --> 00:04:59,120
I get it.

84
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,480
I'm great at this.

85
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:37,720
As expected.

86
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,160
I've lost.

87
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:47,399
You're a formidable opponent too.

88
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,040
Okay, okay, okay.

89
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:54,279
Qiushui City

90
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,560
has chosen to surrender.

91
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,319
With their captain defeated first,

92
00:05:58,439 --> 00:06:00,519
this outcome is understandable.

93
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,680
Indeed.

94
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,720
Now let's look forward to the next match,

95
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,639
Xingguang City versus Frostwind City.

96
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,399
I hereby declare

97
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,480
that Xingguang City

98
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:11,920
forfeits.

99
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:15,920
Xingguang City has also chosen to forfeit.

100
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,519
Frostwind City

101
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,759
forfeits.

102
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,279
Frostwind City's captain has also forfeited.

103
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,519
So that means

104
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,920
Shanhai City wins the championship?

105
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,560
That appears to be the case.

106
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,160
Since Frostwind City forfeited early,

107
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,439
the original schedule has been disrupted.

108
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,839
But sticking to principle,

109
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,839
the finals will still be held in six days,

110
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:37,879
as originally scheduled.

111
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,839
Let's congratulate Shanhai City

112
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:41,680
on earning the right to challenge the Imperial Capital.

113
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,600
Who will win?

114
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,160
Let's wait and see.

115
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,079
Slow down.

116
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:47,839
I'm in a hurry.

117
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,000
What's the rush? My legs are numb.

118
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,360
How can I not be in a hurry?

119
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,839
Any normal person squatting that long,

120
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:52,920
whose legs wouldn't go numb?

121
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,399
I'm walking as fast as I can.

122
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,959
Besides, what good did your coming here do?

123
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:56,959
You'd have lost anyway.

124
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,199
Look at this result.

125
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:02,480
How long were we

126
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,839
in that bathroom anyway?

127
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,199
Strange.

128
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:14,480
Why is the Imperial Capital

129
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:17,439
so insistent on keeping the match schedule?

130
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,720
Throughout this whole tournament,

131
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:22,680
aside from their crazy promotion,

132
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,360
the Imperial Capital doesn't seem

133
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,160
all that invested in the match itself.

134
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:28,800
Even at the venue,

135
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,759
it's just two commentators running things.

136
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:35,199
What role is the Imperial Capital

137
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:38,240
really playing in this match?

138
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:58,199
Speak.

139
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,040
Based on my private investigation

140
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,959
over this past while,

141
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,839
this Gu Changye

142
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:06,360
has been in close contact

143
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,480
with many smaller city heads.

144
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:08,879
As for Gu Changkong,

145
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,199
he's been staying home the whole time,

146
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,079
never showing his face.

147
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:13,319
And every document he's read

148
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,759
has been put through a shredder.

149
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,839
So I

150
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:17,399
specially hired over a hundred people

151
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,680
to collect those paper shreds.

152
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:20,199
It took a massive amount of time

153
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,720
to piece them back into text.

154
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,120
However,

155
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:25,240
most of it was useless information.

156
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,959
But a few keywords among them

157
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,040
were rather interesting.

158
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,199
What keywords?

159
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,279
What lousy tea is this?

160
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,440
Those, those keywords are:

161
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,200
The Second Celestial Advent,

162
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,360
Immortal Summoning,

163
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,440
Immortal Artifact.

164
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:47,919
That's all.

165
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,200
No kidding!

166
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:50,320
Do you know how hard it is

167
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,720
to piece shredded fragments

168
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,039
back into actual text?

169
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,240
If it weren't for yours truly,

170
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,679
you wouldn't have even these few words.

171
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:58,320
Based on this alone,

172
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,679
we can't deduce much yet.

173
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,480
But what's certain is,

174
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:04,200
Gu Changkong and Gu Changye

175
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,240
definitely have their own scheme.

176
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,360
Damn it.

177
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,559
Every crossroad is blocked off.

178
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,279
They're trying to completely cut off

179
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:17,240
any chance I have of leaving the Imperial Capital.

180
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,919
Gu Changye wants me to summon an immortal.

181
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,360
I don't know what he's planning,

182
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,120
but putting my life in someone else's hands,

183
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,240
I can't do that.

184
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:36,240
Should I go find him or not?

185
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:58,679
So you came after all.

186
00:09:58,919 --> 00:09:59,919
You knew I'd come.

187
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:01,919
The Imperial Capital's people

188
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,080
already came to you, didn't they?

189
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,360
You even know about that?

190
00:10:05,879 --> 00:10:06,840
Don't be nervous.

191
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,320
The Imperial Capital's people

192
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:11,240
aren't as merciful as me,

193
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:13,200
letting you go time and again.

194
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,279
So for you,

195
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,879
the most likely outcome will be

196
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,039
death.

197
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:21,159
In all of the Imperial Capital,

198
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:22,960
I'm the only one who can save you.

199
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,279
So unless you're hopelessly stupid,

200
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,440
you were bound to come.

201
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:28,919
Have a seat.

202
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:31,000
Let's have a little chat.

203
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:33,320
What did the Imperial Capital folks tell you?

204
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:40,440
Gu Changye wants me, on the day of the finals,

205
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,639
to summon another immortal.

206
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,879
Gu Changye...

207
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,279
that guy

208
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:51,799
really has some ambition.

209
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:55,200
Let me break it down for you.

210
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:57,080
Gu Changye

211
00:10:57,519 --> 00:10:59,480
plans to, after the match ends,

212
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:01,159
at the awards ceremony,

213
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:03,120
make a move against his own brother.

214
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,080
And you

215
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,039
are one of his trump cards.

216
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:07,879
If he fails,

217
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,720
you'll die right along with him.

218
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,679
And if he succeeds?

219
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,559
You know too much, so you'll die anyway.

220
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,120
So...

221
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:18,200
So you have to save... save me!

222
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,879
Why on earth would I save you?

223
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:22,879
You don't actually think I'm some naive do-gooder, do you?

224
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,039
I have a key.

225
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,559
It can open the Immortal Burial Ground.

226
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:40,759
One key

227
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,200
buys my life.

228
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,080
You should've said so earlier.

229
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,519
I'm a very reasonable man.

230
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:51,240
If you'd handed it over sooner,

231
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,360
you'd probably be on the highway by now.

232
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,759
Could you maybe

233
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:03,960
give me one more little surprise?

234
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:05,080
Like,

235
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,399
The Second Celestial Advent.

236
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,320
I don't know.

237
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:11,759
Are you sure?

238
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,240
I

239
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,360
do have some ancient texts,

240
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,159
which let me get a head start

241
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,039
in the early stages.

242
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:20,159
But that

243
00:12:20,679 --> 00:12:22,320
doesn't mean I know everything.

244
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,000
Just asking.

245
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:25,399
If you don't know, you don't know.

246
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,200
It's not a big deal.

247
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,039
By the way,

248
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,279
do you want to leave right away,

249
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:33,399
or watch the finals first?

250
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:33,960
Now.

251
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,480
Right

252
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,159
this instant.

253
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,200
Alright.

254
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,000
Get him a car.

255
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:42,440
I won't see you out.

256
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:52,120
The Immortal Burial Ground.

257
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:54,519
Wang Qiusheng is gone.

258
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,399
In all my life,

259
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:02,720
no one has ever dared stand me up.

260
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:05,879
Forget it.

261
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:07,879
He was just a bonus anyway.

262
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,759
Once I deal with things here,

263
00:13:10,279 --> 00:13:11,519
I'll go settle the score with him.

264
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,240
You may leave now.

265
00:13:15,679 --> 00:13:17,159
Leave Meiyan to me.

266
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:18,840
Everyone, let's continue.

267
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,600
He's here.

268
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,200
Come, Young Master Gu.

269
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:22,360
This way.

270
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,000
Please sit here.

271
00:13:23,159 --> 00:13:23,919
Everyone, take your seats.

272
00:13:23,919 --> 00:13:25,080
Listen carefully to Young Master Gu.

273
00:13:26,679 --> 00:13:27,960
Tomorrow, after the awards ceremony,

274
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:30,120
when my brother gives his speech,

275
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:31,639
we strike immediately.

276
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,159
Counting my own men,

277
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,919
that's eighty of The Blessed in total.

278
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,960
Gu Changkong will die for sure.

279
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:38,919
I guarantee

280
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,399
that from this day on,

281
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,480
the Imperial Capital will open

282
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:44,360
all trade with all of you,

283
00:13:44,759 --> 00:13:46,919
including financial support.

284
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,840
In that case,

285
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:50,559
Young Master Gu,

286
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,879
we hope from now on

287
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:53,360
you'll look out for us.

288
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,440
Of course.

289
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,000
Yes!

